<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="last-updated"><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 1, 2025</p>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>Welcome to {{ site.name }} ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about how we handle information when you use our website and tools at {{ site.url }} (the "Service").</p>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>Data You Enter Into Our Tools</h3>
  <p><strong>We do not collect, store, or transmit any data you enter into our tools.</strong> All processing happens entirely in your web browser using JavaScript. Your JSON data, passwords, UUIDs, and any other content you generate stays on your device.</p>

  <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
  <p>When you visit our website, we may collect limited technical information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> If you consent to cookies, we use Google Analytics to collect anonymous usage statistics.</li>
    <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> Our hosting provider (Cloudflare) may collect standard web server logs for security and performance purposes.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Cookies and Local Storage</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cookie consent:</strong> We store your cookie preference in local storage.</li>
    <li><strong>Theme preference:</strong> Your dark/light mode preference is stored locally.</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Only if you accept cookies, Google Analytics may set cookies.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>The limited information we collect is used solely to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Improve our tools and user experience</li>
    <li>Understand aggregate usage patterns</li>
    <li>Ensure security and prevent abuse</li>
    <li>Remember your preferences</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
</section>

